OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank boss says 4% inflation
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwon't spark rate cuts      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England's governor has said
OL,6, UK inflation remaining unchanged is    
OL,7, "encouraging", but he hinted it would  
OL,8, not mean earlier interest rate cuts.   
OL,10,FAndrew Bailey said inflation, which    
OL,11,Fmeasures how prices rise over time,    
OL,12,Fstaying at 4% last month "pretty much  
OL,13,Fleaves us where we were".              
OL,15,FThe figure surprised experts who had   
OL,16,Fexpected a rise in energy bills to push
OL,17,Fprices up at a faster rate.            
OL,19,FInvestors have since increased bets    
OL,20,Fthat interest rates will fall in June. 
